---
import BaseLayout from '@layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout
  title="Fireplace Safety — Children, Pets, Clearances | Heat & Glo"
  description="Heat & Glo fireplace safety: protective screens, clearance-to-combustibles, child and pet safety, and proper operation guidelines for every Heat & Glo product."
  noIndex={true}
>
  <!-- HERO -->
  <section class="relative mb-12 -mx-4 overflow-hidden">
    <img
      src="https://hearthnhome.getbynder.com/transform/7c78ef1f-b1af-43cc-9e76-048b67e02a96/HNG_Supreme-30_gas_fireplace_livingroom-1-2x-jpg?io=transform:fill,width:1920,height:720"
      alt="Heat & Glo Supreme 30 gas fireplace in a bright family living room with protective safety screen installed"
      class="w-full h-[600px] md:h-[420px] object-cover"
      loading="eager"
      fetchpriority="high"
    />
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-r from-black/90 via-black/65 to-black/20 flex items-end pb-10 md:items-center md:pb-0 px-6 md:px-8">
      <div class="max-w-page mx-auto text-white">
        <p class="uppercase tracking-widest text-xs font-semibold text-orange-300 mb-3">Fireplace Safety</p>
        <h1 class="text-3xl md:text-3xl md:text-5xl font-bold max-w-2xl leading-tight mb-4">Built to be enjoyed safely.</h1>
        <p class="text-sm md:text-lg text-white/85 max-w-xl mb-8">Every Heat & Glo fireplace is engineered and listed to applicable safety standards. A few practices inside the home make the difference between safe and sorry.</p>
        <div style="display: flex; gap: 16px; flex-wrap: wrap;">
          <a href="/where-to-buy/" style="background: #c44a08; color: #fff; display: inline-block; padding: 14px 28px; border-radius: 8px; font-weight: 700; text-decoration: none; font-size: 15px;" onmouseover="this.style.background='#a83e07'" onmouseout="this.style.background='#c44a08'">Find a dealer to request a safety screen</a>
          <a href="/where-to-buy/" style="background: rgba(255,255,255,0.12); color: #fff; display: inline-block; padding: 14px 28px; border-radius: 8px; font-weight: 600; text-decoration: none; font-size: 15px; border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.35);" onmouseover="this.style.background='rgba(255,255,255,0.22)'" onmouseout="this.style.background='rgba(255,255,255,0.12)'">Find a service dealer</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <main class="max-w-page mx-auto px-4 py-4">

    <!-- INTRO -->
    <header class="mb-12">
      <p class="text-lg text-neutral-700 max-w-2xl">
        Every Heat & Glo fireplace is engineered, tested, and listed to applicable safety standards.
        Real safety in your home depends on a few practices no amount of engineering can replace.
        Read these before your first fire of the season.
      </p>
    </header>

    <!-- SAFETY CARDS WITH IMAGES -->
    <section class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 gap-6 mb-16">
      <div class="border rounded-lg overflow-hidden">
        <img
          src="https://hearthnhome.getbynder.com/transform/bfdcf41c-51d9-4ee9-8420-4fc87fe719ca/happy_couple_discus?io=transform:fill,width:800,height:400"
          alt="Family relaxing near a Heat & Glo fireplace with protective screen installed"
          class="w-full h-44 object-cover"
        />
        <div class="p-6">
          <h2 class="font-semibold text-lg mb-3">Protective screens</h2>
          <p class="text-sm text-neutral-700 leading-relaxed">
            Glass-front gas fireplaces remain hot to the touch for some time after the flame is shut off.
            Heat &amp; Glo protective screens, available as a standard accessory, prevent direct contact
            with hot glass for households with children, pets, or older family members. Strongly
            recommended for any home where vulnerable family members share space with the fireplace.
          </p>
          <a href="/where-to-buy/" class="inline-block mt-4 text-sm font-semibold text-orange-700 underline">
            Request a safety screen through your dealer
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="border rounded-lg overflow-hidden">
        <img
          src="https://hearthnhome.getbynder.com/transform/0a52f87c-2a5e-4be1-97f7-b67c429bae0d/HNG_True_gas_fireplace_livingroom-4-2x-jpg?io=transform:fill,width:800,height:400"
          alt="Heat & Glo True gas fireplace in a traditional living room showing proper clearance and installation"
          class="w-full h-44 object-cover"
        />
        <div class="p-6">
          <h2 class="font-semibold text-lg mb-3">Clearance-to-combustibles</h2>
          <p class="text-sm text-neutral-700 leading-relaxed">
            Every Heat &amp; Glo unit has specific clearance requirements that must be observed when
            installing mantels, surrounds, and adjacent finish materials. Clearances are listed in
            the installation manual for each model. Confirm clearances with your installer before
            finalizing any mantel design.
          </p>
          <a href="/manuals/" class="inline-block mt-4 text-sm font-semibold text-orange-700 underline">
            Find your installation manual
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- INLINE CTA BAND 1 -->
    <section style="background: #1a1a1a; border-radius: 12px; padding: 36px 40px; margin-bottom: 48px; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between; gap: 32px; flex-wrap: wrap;">
      <div>
        <p style="color: #fdba74; font-size: 11px; font-weight: 600; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.1em; margin-bottom: 8px;">Annual service</p>
        <h2 style="color: #fff; font-size: 22px; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 8px;">Schedule your annual inspection.</h2>
        <p style="color: #d1d5db; font-size: 14px; max-width: 480px; line-height: 1.6;">Heat &amp; Glo recommends annual inspection and service of every gas fireplace by a qualified technician. Your authorized dealer can schedule service and confirm wear-component replacements needed for safe operation.</p>
      </div>
      <a href="/where-to-buy/" style="background: #c44a08; color: #fff; display: inline-block; padding: 16px 28px; border-radius: 8px; font-weight: 700; text-decoration: none; white-space: nowrap; font-size: 15px; flex-shrink: 0;" onmouseover="this.style.background='#a83e07'" onmouseout="this.style.background='#c44a08'">Find a service dealer</a>
    </section>

    <!-- ADDITIONAL SAFETY TOPICS WITH IMAGE -->
    <section class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 gap-6 mb-16">
      <div class="border rounded-lg overflow-hidden">
        <img
          src="https://hearthnhome.getbynder.com/transform/937081fe-73df-4957-a0ec-8c5a1bfa3a05/HNG-Primo-II_60-2_2?io=transform:fill,width:800,height:400"
          alt="Contemporary linear fireplace with open floor plan showing recommended furniture clearances"
          class="w-full h-44 object-cover"
        />
        <div class="p-6">
          <h2 class="font-semibold text-lg mb-3">Carbon monoxide and ventilation</h2>
          <p class="text-sm text-neutral-700 leading-relaxed">
            Heat &amp; Glo direct-vent gas fireplaces draw combustion air from outside and exhaust to
            the exterior, maintaining sealed combustion that does not affect indoor air quality when
            installed correctly. Have your vent termination inspected annually for blockages. A
            functioning CO detector in any room with a gas appliance is non-negotiable.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="border rounded-lg overflow-hidden">
        <img
          src="https://hearthnhome.getbynder.com/transform/0cf0665f-d471-4c22-8dc6-3b728e56d262/HNG_Escape_Simply-Aligned-Home_4?io=transform:fill,width:800,height:400"
          alt="Heat & Glo Escape gas insert in a cozy living room showing proper furniture placement and clearance"
          class="w-full h-44 object-cover"
        />
        <div class="p-6">
          <h2 class="font-semibold text-lg mb-3">Proper operation and startup</h2>
          <p class="text-sm text-neutral-700 leading-relaxed">
            Follow the operation procedures in your owner's manual for every seasonal startup. For gas
            units, smell for gas before igniting. For wood units, inspect the firebox and flue before
            the first fire of the season. Never use accelerants. For electric units, ensure the circuit
            is not overloaded and the unit has adequate clearance on all sides.
          </p>
          <a href="/manuals/" class="inline-block mt-4 text-sm font-semibold text-orange-700 underline">
            Download your owner's manual
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- LIFESTYLE INTERSTITIAL -->
    <section class="relative -mx-4 mb-16" style="min-height: 340px;">
      <img
        src="https://hearthnhome.getbynder.com/transform/3bccdcac-d755-40cd-a83e-d15bc37980e1/Pioneer-II_WoodFireplace_Room-SO-tif?io=transform:fill,width:1920,height:520"
        alt="Heat & Glo Pioneer II wood fireplace in a warm family living room with natural stone surround"
        class="w-full object-cover"
        style="height: 340px;"
      />
      <div class="absolute inset-0 flex items-end pb-10 md:items-center md:pb-0 px-6 md:px-8" style="background: rgba(0,0,0,0.55);">
        <div class="max-w-page mx-auto w-full">
          <div style="background: rgba(26,26,26,0.95); padding: 32px 36px; border-radius: 12px; max-width: 34rem; border: 1px solid #333;">
            <p style="color: #fdba74; font-size: 11px; font-weight: 600; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.1em; margin-bottom: 8px;">Engineered since 1975</p>
            <h2 style="color: #fff; font-size: 22px; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 10px;">Safety built in from day one.</h2>
            <p style="color: #d1d5db; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6; margin-bottom: 18px;">Fifty years of engineering means every Heat &amp; Glo unit is tested to applicable UL and ANSI standards before it leaves the facility. Your authorized dealer performs the installation to those same standards.</p>
            <a href="/where-to-buy/" style="background: #c44a08; color: #fff; display: inline-block; padding: 12px 22px; border-radius: 8px; font-weight: 600; text-decoration: none; font-size: 14px;" onmouseover="this.style.background='#a83e07'" onmouseout="this.style.background='#c44a08'">Find an authorized dealer</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- INLINE CTA BAND 2 -->
    <section style="background: #fff7ed; border: 1px solid #fed7aa; border-radius: 12px; padding: 36px 40px; margin-bottom: 64px; display: grid; gap: 24px; grid-template-columns: 2fr 1fr; align-items: center;">
      <div>
        <h2 style="font-size: 22px; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 8px; color: #1a1a1a;">Need annual service or have a safety concern?</h2>
        <p style="color: #6b7280; font-size: 15px;">Your authorized dealer schedules inspections, orders parts, and handles warranty claims. 1,400+ locations across the US and Canada.</p>
      </div>
      <a href="/where-to-buy/" style="background: #c44a08; color: #fff; display: inline-block; padding: 16px 28px; border-radius: 8px; font-weight: 700; text-decoration: none; text-align: center; font-size: 15px;" onmouseover="this.style.background='#a83e07'" onmouseout="this.style.background='#c44a08'">Find your authorized dealer</a>
    </section>

  </main>
</BaseLayout>
